fr:mainmatter.html:div:
  Algorithm: input \theta _t

Sample x_i from dataset \mathcal {D}

Sample z_i(\phi ) \sim  q_{\phi }(\cdot  \mid  x_i, \theta _t) via trick.

Compute \nabla _q \widetilde {\mathsf {ELBO}}

Update via SGD

